            The Warner Music Group Corporation, also known as WMG, is a public company that specializes in national and international repertoire. The company is engaged in recorded music and publishing businesses, as well as manages operations more than 50 countries. It offers artist management, merchandising, touring, VIP ticketing, sponsorship and brand endorsement solutions. The Warner Music Group Corporation also manages a subsidiary, Warner/Chappell Music, which is one of the world's leading music publishers. The subsidiary maintains a catalog of over 1 million songs from nearly 65,000 songwriters. The Warner Music Group Corporation maintains a collection of record labels, including Asylum, Atlantic, Bad Boy and Cordless.
          






















Legal






